Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:12.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn華康中特圓體\fs20\1c&H5E71D7&\pos(498,308)}垃圾入箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:12.39,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fn華康中特圓體\fs20\1c&H5E71D7&\pos(406,370)}節約用水
